title: West Palm Beach Code Enforcement Resignation and Termination Letters

communications.subject: Florida Sunshine Law Request: West Palm Beach Code Enforcement Resignation and Termination Letters
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Florida Sunshine Law, I hereby request the following records:

All letters of resignation and letters of termination in the past 6 months from Code Enforcement.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.
